WEBVTT

00:07.560 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.240 --> 01:42.560
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:48.760 --> 01:50.160
Is all this really necessary?

01:50.680 --> 01:52.280
Weren't you afraid
she'd actually kill you?

01:52.920 --> 01:53.880
Kill me?

01:55.720 --> 01:57.160
It would plunge the court into chaos.

01:58.480 --> 02:00.760
Her Highness was just trying
to humiliate me

02:02.120 --> 02:03.440
and vent her spite.

02:04.960 --> 02:10.080
So, are you breaking the pact
and making her your enemy?

02:11.039 --> 02:12.040
The pact?

02:13.080 --> 02:14.640
Since when has she ever cared for that?

02:15.640 --> 02:19.320
She handed the Imperial Guard Tally
to a nobody from the Xie Family.

02:19.400 --> 02:20.640
Is that her idea of sincerity?

02:21.240 --> 02:23.160
If you had held the Tally,

02:24.200 --> 02:26.360
she would have had
even less chance of survival.

02:34.080 --> 02:35.440
Xiao Xun cannot die.

02:38.720 --> 02:40.000
At least not yet.

02:41.080 --> 02:42.120
Why?

03:01.280 --> 03:03.000
Is this the fallback you mentioned?

03:04.440 --> 03:06.000
The late Emperor's final edict.

03:06.080 --> 03:09.080
Xiao Xun was the designated heir.

03:09.160 --> 03:13.040
It was due to unforeseen complications

03:13.640 --> 03:17.080
that the crown passed to Xiao Yu.

03:19.640 --> 03:20.720
‎ONE DAY EARLIER

03:20.800 --> 03:21.640
Your Highness.

03:24.640 --> 03:28.000
My gates have been so deserted

03:28.520 --> 03:30.760
that even the sparrows
give this place a wide berth.

03:31.480 --> 03:35.120
It is truly rare
that you would actually reach out

03:35.720 --> 03:37.360
to Tie Ying.

03:37.440 --> 03:39.400
Your Highness, have you ever heard

03:40.880 --> 03:42.040
of greatness biding its time
in the depths?

03:46.120 --> 03:47.920
Mr. Deng, are you here

03:48.640 --> 03:52.880
to teach me fortune-reading?

03:53.560 --> 03:57.400
It is a pity
that your judgment has failed you

03:59.400 --> 04:03.400
because there is no greatness
to be found here.

04:05.120 --> 04:08.960
I am naught but a lamb to the slaughter.

04:09.600 --> 04:10.320
No.

04:11.440 --> 04:13.360
I am here to show you

04:15.320 --> 04:17.440
a path to Xiaonan.

04:18.399 --> 04:22.000
Also a path to help reclaim
your former glory.

04:35.680 --> 04:36.840
Why help me?

04:39.640 --> 04:42.400
The imperial court has always been
a treacherous place

04:42.480 --> 04:43.680
of shifting tides.

04:44.200 --> 04:46.720
I don't dare to stake everything
on a single play.

04:46.800 --> 04:50.040
That was true then as it is now.

04:51.920 --> 04:56.680
I am aiding you because I hold
a far more compelling hand.

05:05.400 --> 05:06.960
This is the late Emperor's final edict.

05:07.040 --> 05:09.360
You were the one
meant to inherit the throne.

05:13.120 --> 05:14.760
Indeed, Your Highness.

05:15.280 --> 05:16.560
This is a forgery.

05:16.640 --> 05:19.160
-You…
-But I have the true one, too.

05:20.440 --> 05:22.240
His Majesty has barely
ascended the throne.

05:23.120 --> 05:25.040
Aren't you afraid
of being branded a rebel?

05:27.920 --> 05:31.000
Precision is required to strike,
and clarity is needed to lead.

05:31.520 --> 05:36.040
I aligned with Chu Zhao for a promise

05:36.640 --> 05:40.920
she later broke, prompting my shift
to Your Highness.

05:41.960 --> 05:44.640
My goal has stayed the same throughout.

05:45.360 --> 05:48.480
Are you aware now, Your Highness?

05:51.400 --> 05:56.120
When I claim my destiny,
the seat of Grand Mentor shall be yours.

06:04.640 --> 06:06.200
Mr. Deng, you have a visitor.

06:18.000 --> 06:22.680
So you've prepared your own coffin?

06:23.680 --> 06:25.920
How kind of you to save
the court the expense.

06:26.440 --> 06:29.000
Such prime golden-thread nanmu.

06:29.720 --> 06:31.280
Not really.

06:31.960 --> 06:33.520
It was bestowed by Her Highness.

06:34.120 --> 06:37.160
I heard when the late Emperor
crushed the old dynasty,

06:37.240 --> 06:40.840
the fallen ruler used this very timber

06:41.360 --> 06:43.160
to immolate himself for his state.

06:45.320 --> 06:46.400
I spoke inappropriately.

06:46.480 --> 06:49.800
What brings you here, exactly?

06:52.240 --> 06:53.840
There is a matter

06:54.720 --> 06:59.280
I'm hoping you could shed some light on.

07:07.000 --> 07:08.160
Do you know

07:08.240 --> 07:11.040
Her Highness has besieged
the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan?

07:12.000 --> 07:12.880
Of course.

07:12.960 --> 07:17.640
Do you also know
that Xiao Xun has escaped?

07:17.720 --> 07:18.720
I do.

07:22.240 --> 07:24.360
Do you know

07:26.360 --> 07:27.760
who let him go?

07:28.640 --> 07:29.720
It was me.

07:34.440 --> 07:40.480
Your honesty is quite touching.

07:41.080 --> 07:45.680
Such an act proves
you have turned against Her Highness.

07:46.640 --> 07:51.480
But have you considered
the weight of this coffin?

07:53.800 --> 07:57.840
Can you carry it alone?

07:58.720 --> 08:02.880
You came through the midnight rain
only for this?

08:04.240 --> 08:05.600
I was wondering

08:05.680 --> 08:08.040
if I were the one
letting Xiao Xun walk free,

08:08.640 --> 08:09.680
would she have brought

08:10.480 --> 08:14.600
this coffin
through my Xie Clan's front door?

08:15.800 --> 08:17.160
Mr. Deng,

08:17.240 --> 08:20.400
playing with fire
without a clan's backing is folly.

08:21.880 --> 08:24.480
Beware you don't get burned.

08:25.760 --> 08:27.920
I've long heard your mastery
of the board is unrivaled.

08:28.880 --> 08:30.560
Might I invite you for a round?

08:35.799 --> 08:37.679
It would be my honor.

08:41.400 --> 08:44.280
‎MILITARY CAMP OF YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

08:44.880 --> 08:48.280
General, the Northern Desert forces
know our defenses inside out.

08:48.360 --> 08:50.360
They even have the exact locations
of our hidden sentries.

08:50.440 --> 08:52.560
We must have a traitor.

08:54.000 --> 08:54.960
Report!

08:58.600 --> 09:00.200
Report. Urgent news from the Capital.

09:00.280 --> 09:01.800
Her Highness faces impeachment.

09:01.880 --> 09:03.360
The heir to the Lord of Xiaonan
has fled by night.

09:03.440 --> 09:04.840
Imperial Guard Commander Fu Jiu
is wounded.

09:04.920 --> 09:06.440
Is Jiu's condition severe?

09:06.520 --> 09:09.080
Word is the Imperial Physicians
have consulted, and he is out of danger.

09:09.160 --> 09:10.680
Is Zhao safe and sound?

09:10.760 --> 09:11.680
Her Highness is unharmed.

09:17.760 --> 09:20.960
Xiao Xun fled back to Xiaonan,
and now the Northern Desert invades

09:21.640 --> 09:23.880
with such intimate knowledge
of our defenses.

09:25.760 --> 09:29.000
Could it be a betrayal from within?

09:30.600 --> 09:31.800
Pass the order.

09:31.880 --> 09:34.400
The Third Battalion
is to redeploy to Langya Valley.

09:34.480 --> 09:35.960
The Fifth is to set an ambush
at Yingzui Cliff.

09:36.560 --> 09:38.000
Adjust the defensive line as planned.

09:38.920 --> 09:43.120
Position the hidden troops
and wait for them to take the bait.

09:43.200 --> 09:44.000
-Understood!
-Understood!

09:48.520 --> 09:49.560
General!

09:53.640 --> 09:55.600
General, what is this malady?

09:55.680 --> 09:57.960
It worsens by the day.

09:58.040 --> 09:59.640
Even medicine offers no relief.

10:01.080 --> 10:02.120
It's nothing.

10:03.320 --> 10:06.200
I'll lead the charge tomorrow.

10:06.840 --> 10:08.320
No. You can barely stand.

10:08.400 --> 10:09.680
This is an order.

10:10.960 --> 10:12.120
An order is an order.

10:14.120 --> 10:15.000
Yes.

10:23.760 --> 10:24.840
Your Highness,

10:25.440 --> 10:28.400
Mr. Xie has been recovering here
for three days now.

10:28.920 --> 10:32.160
Though your title leaves
few who dare to criticize you,

10:32.680 --> 10:35.440
the boundaries of decorum remain.

10:35.520 --> 10:39.480
I fear the idle tongues outside
are already beginning to wag.

10:42.720 --> 10:44.400
Since I entered these imperial walls,

10:45.280 --> 10:47.160
when have the rumors ever stopped?

10:49.760 --> 10:54.000
The Censorate is bent on branding me
as "a hen ruling the roost".

10:56.520 --> 10:57.560
Besides,

10:58.320 --> 10:59.640
his injuries are deep.

11:00.160 --> 11:05.600
I won't risk leaving him to others.

11:05.680 --> 11:08.240
Is it because Your Highness
has feelings for him

11:08.760 --> 11:12.120
that you refused to marry Mr. Xiao?

11:16.360 --> 11:19.320
After all our time together,
is that truly how you see me?

11:19.400 --> 11:22.840
No. I spoke out of turn.

11:22.920 --> 11:24.320
Please, do not be angry.

11:28.240 --> 11:32.440
Every string in this palace
must be mine to pull.

11:35.920 --> 11:37.680
But he is more than just a pawn.

11:39.960 --> 11:41.000
He is…

11:43.800 --> 11:44.680
different.

11:45.280 --> 11:46.480
How?

11:49.880 --> 11:51.040
I used him,

11:51.640 --> 11:55.120
and yet, I trust him
more than anyone else.

12:01.160 --> 12:02.120
Regardless,

12:05.000 --> 12:05.920
he is different.

12:10.480 --> 12:11.680
Urgent news from the frontier!

12:11.760 --> 12:13.000
The Northern Desert has attacked Yunzhong.

12:16.640 --> 12:17.520
No.

12:18.960 --> 12:20.400
My report was a forgery.

12:21.760 --> 12:23.080
How could it possibly be real?

12:30.720 --> 12:32.440
Since Her Highness forged the report

12:32.520 --> 12:36.160
of collusion between the Lord of Xiaonan
and the Northern Desert

12:37.040 --> 12:39.920
and tried to drag my family
into this using Pine Soot Ink,

12:40.000 --> 12:41.720
she should have been prepared

12:41.800 --> 12:44.120
for the possibility that her scheme
could spark a real war.

12:45.360 --> 12:46.200
Playing the game,

12:47.000 --> 12:48.600
one must always keep a backup plan.

12:51.840 --> 12:53.480
You look refined,

12:54.800 --> 12:56.240
yet your style of play is ruthless.

12:57.360 --> 12:58.800
You flatter me.

12:59.680 --> 13:02.280
I just dislike wasting time.

13:03.800 --> 13:04.880
However,

13:06.080 --> 13:10.640
patience is the true essence
of Weiqi games.

13:18.640 --> 13:22.800
At the start of this match,
you were full of confidence,

13:23.680 --> 13:24.520
weren't you?

13:29.400 --> 13:31.080
But look at it now.

13:32.160 --> 13:33.920
The situation has changed.

13:41.320 --> 13:45.200
Do my skills meet with your approval?

13:49.920 --> 13:51.920
Your skill…

13:52.840 --> 13:54.840
-is exceptional.
-Good.

13:55.480 --> 13:57.600
Since you enjoy watching,

13:58.120 --> 13:59.960
I shall set several games in motion.

14:00.560 --> 14:02.720
But a board too full
leaves no clear opening.

14:03.840 --> 14:06.960
Beware lest you find no way out.

15:37.400 --> 15:38.480
You're awake.

15:42.240 --> 15:43.880
Are you in any pain?

15:45.920 --> 15:47.640
I failed my mission.

15:49.880 --> 15:51.120
I've dragged you down with me

15:52.160 --> 15:53.360
and gotten you injured.

15:56.640 --> 15:59.080
Deng Yi sent his men
to issue orders at the docks,

15:59.680 --> 16:01.640
which gave Xiao Xun
a chance to escape by water.

16:03.080 --> 16:06.200
I thought it was foolproof.

16:06.720 --> 16:07.640
Yet…

16:10.040 --> 16:14.080
The game at court is never that simple.

16:15.280 --> 16:16.800
Such is the nature of power.

16:17.640 --> 16:18.800
Tell me.

16:18.880 --> 16:20.520
How do you want me to repay this debt?

16:21.120 --> 16:22.840
I can grant you one wish.

16:30.760 --> 16:32.840
I've never believed in divinity.

16:33.480 --> 16:34.320
I have no wishes.

16:35.960 --> 16:39.320
Then is there nothing you wish to achieve?

16:44.680 --> 16:45.520
No.

16:47.560 --> 16:48.640
Very well.

16:48.720 --> 16:51.400
Then let the debt stand for now.

16:52.000 --> 16:55.440
When you decide what you want,
just come to me.

17:08.079 --> 17:10.720
With your skills,
you shouldn't be this badly hurt.

17:12.440 --> 17:15.040
What really happened that day?

17:18.839 --> 17:19.800
Tie Ying

17:21.839 --> 17:23.200
used hidden weapons.

17:24.800 --> 17:26.720
I let my guard down and got ambushed.

17:27.240 --> 17:28.160
Just as I thought.

17:29.120 --> 17:31.120
They only resort
to such despicable tricks.

17:37.720 --> 17:39.280
Last night, I saw you having a nightmare.

17:40.360 --> 17:41.880
You seemed burdened by something.

17:43.120 --> 17:44.240
As you said,

17:45.520 --> 17:47.880
everyone has their own secrets.

17:49.040 --> 17:52.360
True. But I shared mine with you.

17:53.840 --> 17:55.960
You mean that dream?

18:06.600 --> 18:07.520
Alright.

18:08.160 --> 18:09.360
As an exchange,

18:10.760 --> 18:11.880
I'll tell you a secret.

18:19.960 --> 18:20.840
Actually…

18:25.520 --> 18:26.600
I…

18:35.680 --> 18:40.080
CAPITAL

18:55.720 --> 18:58.600
I once sneaked a bite of the jujube cakes
you got for your father

18:59.120 --> 19:00.160
and paid for it with a beating.

19:02.080 --> 19:03.640
Thank you for sharing that.

19:05.080 --> 19:06.120
It's just…

19:07.800 --> 19:09.680
I'll never make that again.

19:16.120 --> 19:17.080
No matter.

19:18.560 --> 19:20.520
I never liked those pastries anyway.

19:23.600 --> 19:26.880
I was thinking of making you
something else to eat.

19:29.200 --> 19:30.040
Sounds good.

19:55.640 --> 19:58.440
Jiu, my hairpin is a bit askew.

19:58.960 --> 20:00.400
Fix it for me, would you?

21:46.040 --> 21:46.920
Good, right?

21:47.520 --> 21:50.040
Six hours at the stove,
steamer after steamer,

21:50.560 --> 21:51.640
all for a flawless batch.

21:53.240 --> 21:56.480
It's truly the finest delicacy
in the world.

21:57.160 --> 21:58.960
You should've mixed the filling properly.

21:59.760 --> 22:01.600
The ratio of lard has to be exact.

22:02.120 --> 22:03.400
Too little or too much ruins it.

22:05.000 --> 22:05.960
I see.

22:06.640 --> 22:07.960
My father always said

22:08.040 --> 22:10.960
too little makes it dry
and too much makes it greasy.

22:20.720 --> 22:22.520
It's my fault.

22:25.520 --> 22:27.480
I have been away from Yunzhong for so long

22:30.000 --> 22:31.080
that I have forgotten

22:35.000 --> 22:36.360
the recipe.

22:38.240 --> 22:39.360
In fact,

22:40.280 --> 22:41.440
I was never very skilled

22:43.520 --> 22:45.320
at making these pastries to begin with.

22:50.640 --> 22:52.800
Father, see? I made it.

22:52.880 --> 22:54.640
I finally mastered jujube cakes.

22:56.400 --> 22:58.320
Well done.

22:59.800 --> 23:02.240
Just try not to sneak
the filling next time.

23:08.480 --> 23:10.880
<i>Father, don't scare me.</i>
<i>I just missed my mother.</i>

23:11.520 --> 23:13.800
I didn't grow up by her side,
so I wanted to take a look.

23:14.480 --> 23:17.320
To look at the sights she saw
and walk the lanes she walked.

23:17.400 --> 23:19.640
If Mother were still alive,

23:19.720 --> 23:22.360
she wouldn't want me
to be an obedient girl.

23:22.960 --> 23:24.560
She wouldn't be as arrogant as you.

23:25.760 --> 23:27.560
<i>She would care about my feelings.</i>

23:28.560 --> 23:32.400
<i>Yeah. You're the undefeated God of War.</i>

23:32.480 --> 23:34.320
<i>You're the esteemed Guard General.</i>

23:34.400 --> 23:36.440
<i>You're busy protecting frontier people.</i>

23:36.520 --> 23:38.840
<i>You're busy forging your fame.</i>

23:38.920 --> 23:40.040
<i>You're too busy</i>

23:40.120 --> 23:43.480
<i>to ask your daughter</i>
<i>what she really wants!</i>

23:48.120 --> 23:51.560
Missing someone
is nothing to be ashamed of.

23:55.160 --> 23:56.560
And neither is being homesick.

24:17.360 --> 24:18.880
During the years I spent
by your father's side,

24:20.240 --> 24:21.400
he seemed truly content.

24:23.280 --> 24:24.800
He kept himself busy,

24:26.880 --> 24:28.800
but whenever he got rare spices
from the Western Regions,

24:30.200 --> 24:32.080
he would tuck them away
in the room at the southern courtyard.

24:33.360 --> 24:34.640
When he went out on patrol,

24:35.480 --> 24:37.000
if he saw a lovely sprig of blossoms,

24:37.920 --> 24:41.520
he would bring it back
to plant in that courtyard.

24:42.440 --> 24:46.360
He told me it was where you once lived,

24:47.080 --> 24:48.560
and so he kept it in order
for your return.

24:54.720 --> 24:56.080
Chu Zhao.

24:59.080 --> 25:00.320
Your father never blamed you

25:01.600 --> 25:02.720
for your leaving.

25:04.640 --> 25:05.880
He only wanted to know

25:06.480 --> 25:07.800
whether you were doing well.

25:10.000 --> 25:11.440
He has missed you, that's all.

25:13.720 --> 25:17.480
You don't have to respond to any of this.

25:18.920 --> 25:20.400
These are his feelings to carry.

25:22.360 --> 25:23.720
So please don't be too hard on yourself.

25:25.000 --> 25:28.440
No one needs to be forgiven.

25:30.040 --> 25:31.000
Actually,

25:33.960 --> 25:35.560
I miss him terribly too

25:37.440 --> 25:39.160
and everything about the desert.

25:45.280 --> 25:48.160
He is a man of stern discipline

25:49.280 --> 25:50.360
yet with a tender heart.

25:53.560 --> 25:54.400
Much like you.

26:02.400 --> 26:05.280
The first time he took me
to the desert poplar forest,

26:05.960 --> 26:08.280
he said every withered branch there

26:09.200 --> 26:10.840
was fighting desperately to stay alive,

26:11.520 --> 26:13.360
which is what shaped
this timeless landscape.

26:15.520 --> 26:16.800
Dying is easy.

26:20.560 --> 26:22.080
Living takes true strength.

26:24.480 --> 26:25.360
Jiu.

26:28.280 --> 26:29.240
My apologies.

26:30.200 --> 26:31.120
I've said too much.

26:32.000 --> 26:32.920
Not at all.

26:34.880 --> 26:38.520
I'm glad to hear you speak your mind.

26:42.240 --> 26:43.200
It's late and cold.

26:44.320 --> 26:45.400
Please get some rest, Your Highness.

26:46.840 --> 26:47.920
Thank you

26:49.520 --> 26:51.600
for telling me about my father

26:52.760 --> 26:54.960
and for sharing your past with me.

26:56.840 --> 26:57.680
You are welcome.

26:59.600 --> 27:01.000
Consider it repayment

27:02.840 --> 27:03.680
for that pastry.

27:07.240 --> 27:10.680
Then please take this box
of red bean cakes.

27:12.120 --> 27:13.160
I appreciate it.

27:15.080 --> 27:16.720
What I said today still stands.

27:19.880 --> 27:21.160
From now on,

27:21.960 --> 27:24.840
whatever wish you hold,
you may ask it of me.

27:25.520 --> 27:27.440
Come fire or high water,

27:27.960 --> 27:29.520
I will see it fulfilled.

27:33.840 --> 27:37.560
I honor my promises and never renege.

27:40.000 --> 27:42.800
Alright. I understand.

27:44.520 --> 27:45.520
Report!

27:47.080 --> 27:47.920
Report!

27:49.480 --> 27:51.280
Your Highness, urgent news from Yunzhong.

27:51.360 --> 27:52.880
<i>The Northern Desert invaded yesterday.</i>

27:52.960 --> 27:55.360
<i>General Chu drove them back,</i>
<i>but collapsed shortly after.</i>

27:55.440 --> 27:56.560
<i>He hasn't woken up.</i>

27:58.960 --> 28:00.760
General. The enemy has withdrawn!

28:01.560 --> 28:03.720
Exactly as you predicted.

28:03.800 --> 28:06.320
Your foresight secured our victory.

28:15.360 --> 28:16.400
General.

28:27.600 --> 28:30.720
‎LORD OF XIAONAN'S MANOR

28:41.880 --> 28:42.720
Father.

28:49.800 --> 28:50.800
Are you hurt?

28:53.520 --> 28:54.520
You may not know,

28:55.120 --> 28:58.640
but Chu Ling's daughter
seeks to finish me off for good.

28:59.240 --> 29:00.840
Chu Ling's daughter?

29:02.120 --> 29:03.680
The one who refused to marry you

29:03.760 --> 29:05.240
and only ever wanted
to be the Grand Princess?

29:07.080 --> 29:09.200
The throne changes and chaos follows.

29:10.080 --> 29:12.480
We and Yunzhong hold each other in check.

29:13.320 --> 29:15.080
The Xie Clan of Gaoyang
eyes us with greed.

29:16.280 --> 29:19.040
Yet she moved first to purge
our army in the Capital,

29:19.960 --> 29:22.720
then used your plight
to build her power in the court.

29:23.760 --> 29:27.240
Such methods are truly masterful.

29:27.320 --> 29:31.200
This upheaval plunges
the Capital into chaos.

29:31.880 --> 29:34.280
-Perhaps we…
-The essence of alchemy lies

29:34.360 --> 29:36.400
within the mastery of fire.

29:37.240 --> 29:38.960
When the Yellow Emperor
forged his cauldron,

29:39.040 --> 29:41.400
the Loong's roar emerged after 49 days.

29:41.480 --> 29:45.080
When the alchemists refined mercury,
the rosy aura condensed after 81 nights.

29:45.160 --> 29:47.680
It all comes down to the precise moment.

29:48.200 --> 29:51.440
Opening the cauldron
before completion risks failure.

29:53.640 --> 29:54.960
‎LORD OF XIAONAN, XIAO HONG

29:55.040 --> 29:57.240
You must be weary from the road.

29:57.760 --> 29:58.880
Get some rest.

30:01.120 --> 30:02.000
Yes.

30:16.080 --> 30:17.560
General Chu Ling

30:17.640 --> 30:21.200
shall be held negligent
for the Northern Desert's incursion.

30:22.080 --> 30:23.960
Yes, they breached our frontiers,

30:24.680 --> 30:26.960
but it is also true General Chu
led them into a void.

30:27.040 --> 30:30.120
No reward for his merit,
yet only a trial for his fault?

30:30.800 --> 30:32.200
Since he took command,

30:32.280 --> 30:35.280
victory has been his solemn duty.

30:35.360 --> 30:37.240
Had Yunzhong fallen,

30:37.320 --> 30:39.120
the consequences
would've been catastrophic.

30:39.200 --> 30:41.520
Merit cannot offset such a grave failing.

30:42.360 --> 30:43.280
Your Majesty,

30:43.800 --> 30:45.440
Chu Ling has been lax
in disciplining his troops

30:46.080 --> 30:47.440
and must be held to account.

30:47.520 --> 30:51.520
-Seconded.
-Seconded.

30:52.880 --> 30:55.800
Chamberlain, your concern
for the state is commendable.

30:55.880 --> 30:57.400
But I must ask this.

30:58.000 --> 31:00.920
No sooner had Xiao Xun
fled back to Xiaonan,

31:01.560 --> 31:03.240
than the invasion happened.

31:04.000 --> 31:05.200
Is this striking coincidence

31:05.920 --> 31:07.920
proof of collusion from within?

31:09.440 --> 31:11.880
Your Highness reminded me of something.

31:11.960 --> 31:13.840
As I recall,

31:13.920 --> 31:16.120
Mr. Deng argued most fervently
for Xiao Xun's pardon,

31:16.960 --> 31:18.040
claiming it was to appease

31:18.680 --> 31:20.360
the Lord of Xiaonan.

31:21.040 --> 31:25.000
Such impeccable timing
for a show of mercy.

31:26.320 --> 31:27.800
Watch your words, Mr. Xie.

31:28.320 --> 31:32.680
His Majesty decreed
Xiao Xun's pardon and return.

31:33.280 --> 31:35.640
Who am I to challenge the throne?

31:36.800 --> 31:41.280
Word has it you've set your sights

31:42.520 --> 31:43.960
on Xiao Xun's residence.

31:44.040 --> 31:47.400
It is a place of great vantage.

31:47.480 --> 31:50.520
Better to use it than waste it.

31:51.520 --> 31:53.600
His Majesty, in his infinite mercy,
bestowed it upon me.

31:53.680 --> 31:54.760
What?

31:56.320 --> 31:58.560
-You wish for it as well?
-Enough.

31:59.240 --> 32:02.120
With the Northern Desert encroaching,
our priority is to steady the troops.

32:03.280 --> 32:04.720
As for the cancer within…

32:09.720 --> 32:12.160
I shall see for myself

32:13.000 --> 32:17.320
who is so desperate to usher in the enemy.

32:21.440 --> 32:22.280
I am weary.

32:23.200 --> 32:25.800
Should you have no other matters,
you may take your leave.

32:27.000 --> 32:28.560
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty

32:28.640 --> 32:30.360
-and Your Highness.
-and Your Highness.

32:54.920 --> 32:57.040
Who would have thought Xie Yanfang

32:57.920 --> 33:00.160
would show his hand so brazenly?

33:01.640 --> 33:03.000
Since he dared tell you

33:03.080 --> 33:06.680
he would bring
the Grand Princess a true war,

33:06.760 --> 33:08.760
he clearly fears nothing,

33:09.280 --> 33:10.800
knowing we lack the evidence

33:11.440 --> 33:13.240
to move against him.

33:15.080 --> 33:16.000
Indeed.

33:16.920 --> 33:20.880
The very fact he said it proves
he has a contingency plan in place.

33:21.920 --> 33:23.560
Even if we sent men to investigate now,

33:24.480 --> 33:25.960
they would find nothing.

33:26.760 --> 33:29.080
Xie Yanfang is guarded
like an iron fortress.

33:30.040 --> 33:31.840
But even the tightest defense has a flaw.

33:32.520 --> 33:36.040
Why not start by digging
into his place in Gaoyang?

33:36.560 --> 33:38.160
When he came to the Capital,

33:39.200 --> 33:41.520
he brought all his men with him.

33:42.040 --> 33:45.840
The rest at the Gaoyang estate
are of no consequence.

33:46.440 --> 33:47.520
You are right, though.

33:48.200 --> 33:50.080
To strike at the heart of the threat,

33:51.040 --> 33:53.400
one must first brave the lion's den.

33:57.920 --> 33:58.840
Shao You.

34:05.000 --> 34:06.640
Send men to Gaoyang at once.

34:07.560 --> 34:08.400
Understood.

34:12.239 --> 34:13.239
Mr. Xie,

34:14.360 --> 34:18.440
better mind your moves in this game.

34:19.639 --> 34:22.320
PRINCE XIAO XUN'S RESIDENCE

34:24.360 --> 34:26.520
Move more to the left. Higher.

34:26.600 --> 34:28.199
XIE RESIDENCE

34:28.280 --> 34:30.320
That's it. Get down.

34:32.560 --> 34:34.000
With that plaque in place,

34:34.600 --> 34:36.440
the whole estate seems brighter.

34:36.520 --> 34:39.440
Mr. Xie, rumors have it

34:39.520 --> 34:42.040
Guard General Chu Ling's negligence
allowed the breach.

34:42.120 --> 34:47.000
Do you think he'd be like Xiao Xun,
colluding with the enemy?

34:47.840 --> 34:51.600
If Xiao could survive such dire straits,
so can he.

34:52.360 --> 34:54.480
Having spent years at the frontier
with an undefeated record,

34:55.000 --> 34:56.880
the prestige he holds among the people

34:56.960 --> 34:59.240
can not be undone by a single lapse
in judgment.

35:00.040 --> 35:02.520
We may have orchestrated the invasion,

35:03.200 --> 35:07.760
but his swift tactical shift
lured the enemy to Xinggu Pass

35:08.800 --> 35:10.520
and secured a total victory.

35:11.040 --> 35:14.400
Many now laud his braveness and mind.

35:16.320 --> 35:20.840
It seems we've only served
to further his renown.

35:22.080 --> 35:23.080
True.

35:23.160 --> 35:24.840
Just as you are renowned
throughout the land.

35:24.920 --> 35:27.040
Though away from court for years,

35:27.120 --> 35:28.960
your foundation remains unshakable.

35:30.160 --> 35:31.000
No.

35:32.960 --> 35:33.960
He and I…

35:35.080 --> 35:36.600
have never been the same.

35:38.280 --> 35:39.840
Since the estate is renovated,

35:40.960 --> 35:42.280
send for Yanlai.

35:42.800 --> 35:48.440
Tell him it is the Master's command
that he return at once.

35:48.520 --> 35:51.440
He's always been at odds with your family.

35:51.520 --> 35:52.360
Why this?

35:53.200 --> 35:54.320
I am merely curious.

35:57.520 --> 35:59.680
After five years, does the hound…

36:01.440 --> 36:03.400
still know its leash?

36:05.880 --> 36:07.360
Blessings and calamities coexist.

36:07.440 --> 36:10.200
Great fortune is accompanied
by great danger.

36:10.280 --> 36:11.040
‎CHU TANG, COUSIN OF CHU ZHAO

36:11.120 --> 36:13.720
This title may not prove to be

36:13.800 --> 36:16.600
a shield for the Chu Family.

36:18.440 --> 36:21.840
Of course,
I am grateful for Uncle's care years ago.

36:22.600 --> 36:23.760
It's just…

36:26.080 --> 36:27.720
Should I fall from this height,

36:28.360 --> 36:31.880
as family, you will
inevitably be implicated.

36:33.160 --> 36:37.160
So, you'd better plot your own course.

36:38.120 --> 36:40.280
Zhao, no need to test me.

36:41.240 --> 36:43.800
From the day you attained this title,

36:44.720 --> 36:51.120
the Chu Family rises and falls with you.

36:52.960 --> 36:53.800
Very well.

36:55.960 --> 36:56.960
Then,

37:06.240 --> 37:09.360
from now on,
I shall maneuver in the light,

37:10.040 --> 37:11.360
while you operate in the shadows.

37:12.080 --> 37:15.160
I'll be your fortress,
and you'll be my reach.

37:15.240 --> 37:19.360
If we win, we shall share
in glory and splendor.

37:20.400 --> 37:21.320
If we fail…

37:29.600 --> 37:31.360
I am yours to command.

37:32.960 --> 37:35.280
Please keep faith with your pledge.

37:36.040 --> 37:37.120
After this tea,

37:37.880 --> 37:39.480
there is no turning back.

37:47.200 --> 37:48.400
<i>Now that I depart the Capital,</i>

37:48.480 --> 37:52.960
<i>I must rally every available ally</i>
<i>to hold the court for me.</i>
